'''Aẓawan amaziɣ'''<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref> ; [ [[G.M|G.T]] '':''  ''"[[Ẓ (Askkil)|ẓ]]" tga tuffayt, illa mad as ittinin "Azawan", ar ttyara s yaẓ maci yaz'' ] (s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|Tfransist]] : la musique berbère; s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|Tasrɣint]] : الموسيقى الأمازيغية). iga uẓawan amaziɣ yan wanaw iẓlin n uẓawan, illa wanaw ad g tmizar timaziɣin (n [[Tamazɣa|tmazɣa]])  ili ula g tmizar yaḍni da g llan tugt n [[Anmaddu|inmudda]]<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref> imaziɣn, zund ukan [[Fransa|Franṣa]], [[Ṣbanya|Spanya]], [[Iwankn Munnin n Marikan|Marikan]], [[Kanaḍa]], [[Israyil|Israil]] ...[[Ar tigira]]. 

Akud nna nsawal f uẓawan amaziɣ, at ar nsawwal f yan igr bahra imqqurn d ar nsawwal f uẓawan issmrasn tutlayt tamaziɣtn imassn imaziɣn, tamdyazt tamaziɣt ...A.T. G umaḍal n ɣassad nzzḍar a nisan tirruyṣa, tagruppit g tmazirt n [[Sus]]; tamawayt, tahidust g tmazirt n [[Ẓayyan|ẓayyan,]] nzzdaṛ ula a nsawl ula f uḥidus, aḥwac. Macc tidt<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref> tugr mayad, acku aẓawan amaziɣ ggutn gis wanawn. 

Aẓawan amaziɣ issn g umzruy ns tugt n uzzigz d ussnfl, illa uẓawan aqqbur, azayku d uẓawan atrar. Ur ittyawssan man uzmz a issnti uẓawan amaziɣ acku zugn warratn g igr ad. Illa ma ittinin mas [[Lḥaj Blɛid|Lhaj Blɛid]] iga sg imzwwra da issntin g uẓawan amaziɣ macc iggut wawwal.

== Tirruysa (Rrways) : ==
Taga tirruysa (nɣ [[Rrways]]) anaw da bahra ittyawssan dar iclḥin n [[Sus]] d ma srs izdin g tmnaḍin. iẓli wanaw ad f wanawn yaḍni, iẓli g imassn ns, g uṭṭun n middn gis ittilin d wassaɣn nsn, acku anaw ad nzzḍar a nini mas iga sg uẓawan aqqbur ikkad tusutin inɣuban n umzruy. Annay amzwaru n tirruysa illa f ufus n [[Lḥaj Blɛid]] acku nttan a isskcmn anaw ad s [[imassn n unyalkam]] (Lkaṣiṭ n lvidyu), macc izzḍar a ili urta ilul Lḥaj Blɛid. 

ittyusmma wanaw ad Tirruysa acku amɣar n trabbut ismas "Rrays", ilin dis tugt n middn yaḍni (irgazn nɣ timɣarin). imassn n Rrways ẓlin bahra, ar tturarn s [[Ribab|Rribab]].

